The MP2 Avant-garde ruleset is a modernized ruleset to take advantage of cutting-edge advancements in Freeciv Server development. 
It is more advanced than the previous MP-branch rulesets. It imports features, improvements, and novel ideas from all other versions
of Freeciv, later versions of the commercial series, and original ideas from top-tier players.

This ruleset began using multiplayer as its base and evolved from it. Enjoy!

